{"tid":837075,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國撕破面皮　中資港股　修改章程大設黨委　香港股市不再自由","createTime":"2018-09-26T06:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T17:05:18.000Z","uid":47714,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"adf5db1ba67ce1662513056cf35e0aa3a40b3586","tid":837075,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:08:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/hit/daily/article/20180926/20508207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fhit%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180926%2F20508207&d=GLlPsK05qGU%2FIJO3gfn48pUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=524373c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fhit%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180926%2F20508207&h=b70ee113\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/hit/daily/article/20180926/20508207</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/video/20180926/720pix/1537904607_09b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20180926%2F720pix%2F1537904607_09b8.jpg&h=c5d0ac8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共總書記兼國家主席習近平要做到全方位控制，黨的手影已全面滲透香港上市公司界別。本報對本港上市公司進行全面統計，發現去年至今，有123間上市公司通過修改公司章程，正式確立黨委（即共產黨委員會）及給予權力，佔港交所2,262間（包括382間創業板）上市公司5.43%，其中有8間屬恒生指數成份股（俗稱藍籌股）。<br />\n<br />\n這個「改姓黨」的風潮仍未息止，直至上周四仍不斷有國企、央企修改章程，部份公司越改越過份，將黨委權力任意放大。有公司講明黨委經費要佔員工薪酬總額1%；有的指黨委若發現公司不符黨路線，可向上級黨組織報告。當出現利益衝突，黨的利益一定凌駕於股東利益之上，維權投資者David Webb斥責，港交所放行其大客─中國政府，將潛規則變成白紙黑字的「永久性」公司條文，做法離譜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/224672/【買起香港】股市1：在港上市中資廿年飆14倍　恆/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F224672%2F%E3%80%90%E8%B2%B7%E8%B5%B7%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%91%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%821%EF%BC%9A%E5%9C%A8%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E5%BB%BF%E5%B9%B4%E9%A3%8614%E5%80%8D%E3%80%80%E6%81%86%2F&d=GLlPsK05qGU%2FIJO3gfn48pUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=cd74eced\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/224672/【買起香港】股市1：在港上市中資廿年飆14倍　恆/</a><br />\n<br />\n恆指中資股數目破半　總比重壓倒港股<br />\n<br />\n恆生指數成份股近年來的變動，也可見中資逐步「侵占」香港股市的痕跡。恆指成份股過往維持於50隻，中資佔半數，但今年2月，恒生指數公司宣布將利豐（494）剔除，並將吉利汽車（175）納入成份股後，港資與中資的比例便成為24:26。不過今年7月，屬中資的百麗國際（1880）被剔出名單，中資股減一隻，但由於未有增補新股，港資與中資仍維持24:25的比例。<br />\n<br />\n至於比重方面，在比重最大的10隻成份股中，便有6隻屬中資。恆指目前49隻成份股總比重為99.96，25隻中資成份股佔當中的53.23，相等於53.25%；24隻港資成份股則佔46.73，相等於近46.75%。由此可見，中資與港資在恆指的影響力，其實絕對不止「24:25」一隻成份股的差微差距。"},{"pid":"5f51bdf48d7e6e4bc47b00bae837ace1bfc8191a","tid":837075,"uid":144626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"等睇hsi畀美國dq"},{"pid":"9fa9deb993bbeea05673ce5edbc88e7373f120b8","tid":837075,"uid":37240,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:10:04.000Z","msg":"肉酸死<br />\n比美國打到呀媽都唔認得<br />\n就要去搜刮民脂民膏<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee6675c3c658e2cfb6fbe63279fb6dc5c317802","tid":837075,"uid":62532,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"屌咁搞法外資仲留hk做乜"},{"pid":"f41cb7910e7e8dd876d1880dde13fa9a84b8bdef","tid":837075,"uid":66943,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:11:34.000Z","msg":"黨大過關係法<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57f708f15ab1c7e2c0fa310f9d3e3b6fee2abf9","tid":837075,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f9924b3434f8348fe0bdd6c11cba1928e9aa3d","tid":837075,"uid":210031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:12:44.000Z","msg":"咁搞法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇眼睇"},{"pid":"c614a4cf6c96e1ea6a1aed6b4958b8d4d6b8d50d","ti